{
  "stem": "26142.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We stayed there for an hour or two, I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All of a sudden, Ukrainian people came, young people, and they saw this wonder, that there are a few hundred people-- men, women, and children-- on a field.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they introduced themselves, two guys, they introduced themselves that they are this sons of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], in Ukrainian, means the mayor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those are the mayor's sons, and we should go with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They will place us in certain places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We should go with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't know where to go, so we went with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the name of the village I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't remember the name of the village, but those two guys, they started to separate families, and they left in-- the farmers that were there, they had huge barns, where they even were having outside where they treated their grain in the yards.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we fell in, my brother Tsvi, and Moishe, with his children, and I, and a family that was from Budapest, a mother, a son, and a daughter.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This son was a violinist that played in the Budapest orchestra and lived there for 30 or some years.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they, evidently, somehow they didn't have Hungarian citizenship.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even though they lived in Hungary, the didn't have Hungarian citizenship, and they were-- somehow, how they got there, they were attached to us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they led us into this [NON-ENGLISH] barn.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in that barn we had already-- there was a little straw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were totally exhausted from all this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is a week, now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we started asking-- we had some Hungarian money-- if we can buy something.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
